item.title: Help plz [delta317]
item.dc:creator: @pure2ownage Pure_
item.description:
@pure2ownage wrote:

open up ClickingMost.java and search for the coords of an previous teleport or the message it sends once you click on it.
Example:-

sM("you teleport home");

then you will search for the words “you teleport home”, above or below it will be something like toX = 3333; toY = 3333; that is the coordinates, change that and the message if you may and compile ;D
